timing_disabl...kperiod_checks(25.10)    timing_disabl...kperiod_checks(25.10)

Name
       timing_disable_clockperiod_checks

Syntax
       timing_disable_clockperiod_checks

       {true | false}

       Default: false (performs checks)

       When set to true, disables timing model clock period checks during tim-
       ing analysis.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

